Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:49.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm going back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you hear, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be quiet, will ya?\NJust go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:57.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every time you return,\nyou two get into some argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:00.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Granny Kaede,\nplease take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha,\nare you just going to let her go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:08.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:20.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I only stopped the fight because\NI was worried about your injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:27.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please be patient, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha always gets jealous over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:33.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome, you're my woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:36.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is small-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:39.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why he takes Koga's\nwords so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's a pitiful fool who is\nactually very insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:46.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And because he's so in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:51.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm just going back to get\nmore medicine and bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:55.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.\NBut don't tell Inuyasha that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:00.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sometimes,\nit's good to make him worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:05.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! I understand.\NKagome, please return quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku... what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:47.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sharp as usual, Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could I not notice you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:55.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only today, you've come\nto spy on me countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:59.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You seem to be quite\nconcerned about me, Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:07.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku... You can't help but\nbe concerned about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:08.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:13.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo's heart beats strong\nwithin you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:37.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:38.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to eat?\NOr do you want a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You look so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I'll run your bath right now.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, now... put down your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:05:00.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe that was a conversation\nbetween a mother and a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:03.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More like a husband who's been away\non assignment and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:15.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, how long are you staying\nthis time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take a nap, then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Sota...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,can you get me the\nbandages and antibiotics?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:29.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... A bed is {\i1}sooo{\i0} nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:33.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll make sure that Inuyasha\nworries a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:53.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku... You can't help but\nbe concerned about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:06:00.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onigumo's heart beats\nstrong within you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:04.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A woman like that\ncan be killed off anytime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the reason I can't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is that because within me\nstill beats...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:14.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the heart of that Onigumo\nwho so coveted Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onigumo's heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That shallow, evil criminal...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was unable to move...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:27.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet he yearned for Kikyo\nso much...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that he offered his body to\ncountless demons...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}to be reborn as Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:49.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That foolish human's heart\nstill yearns for Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it still beats inside me...Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ludicrous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You belittle me, Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I, Naraku, am not Onigumo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:11.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I have the Sacred Jewel\nnearly whole...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:16.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I find Onigumo's heart useless\nand unnecessary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that dark cloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:59.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been hovering over the temple\nfor a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:11.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those lights...lost souls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:16.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's devouring the lost souls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:23.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku...is coming after me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kikyo, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need to borrow your horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:48.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That demon...does he intend to eat\nall the lost souls in this region?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:49.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will not allow it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! It took lost souls from me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:06.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, how is your wound?\NDoes it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to the care you\nand Kaede have given me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:15.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Naraku has many incarnations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:18.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're talking about\NJuromaru and Kageromaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:22.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fourth incarnation,\NJuromaru, the younger sibling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:25.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting is his only volition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He won't even heed Naraku's orders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though the Naraku that was\nhandling him was a demon puppet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Juromaru ruthlessly chopped off\NNaraku's head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:39.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Naraku seemed to have\ntrouble controlling him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:44.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alongwith Kageromaru, the oldersibling,\nwho hides inside Juromaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They were both brutal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and so mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:52.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't know what kind of\nenemy will attack next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:57.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must be even more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:02.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say Inuyasha... aren't you going to\ncall Kagome back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! We're better off without her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then,\ncan you stop your fidgeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's really irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is so patient\nin dealing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:22.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I couldn't agree more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm just going back\nfor more bandages and medicine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be right back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But don't tell Inuyasha that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's good to make him worry sometimes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promised Kagome.\NI'll keep quiet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,\NKoga's love is one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No need to be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listening to you all talk,\nit's as though it's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:57.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't apologize! Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just 'cuz you didn't come\nback right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm getting all the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'd I do anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:29.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome,\nare you angry with me, after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what she's doing now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:39.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A demon's scent!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- what's that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A giant soul collector?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:51.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're badly hurt!\NWhat happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poison insects?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this another one of\NNaraku's tricks?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:10.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-where is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He plans to get rid of Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't allow it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if I'd allow Naraku\nto kill Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo... I'll take care of that demon\nright away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So stay quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:58.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is your death sentence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without the souls of the dead,\nyou cannot stay alive... Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:00.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon came after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you came here hoping\nthat I'd save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I kept running desperately\nand found myself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:23.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:53.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's night already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:59.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why didn't anyone wake me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:01.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fifty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:13.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We haven't changed at all\nsince fifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:22.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silly words... I have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:27.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since that time\NI sealed you against this tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:31.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of Naraku's deception,\nwe hated each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I was sealed here\non this tree for fifty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:42.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, tell me, have I changed then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:51.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before I knew of Naraku's existence,\NI did resent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:55.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you told me\nthat my life was yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:58.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're no different\nfrom Naraku, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:13.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm the same... as Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inside Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo's heart still beats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo's heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:26.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That evil man desired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Killing you with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:34.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}was something that the jealous heart\nof Onigumo schemed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jealous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over something so ridiculous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:40.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:44.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is what humans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:49.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onigumo's heart remains\ninside Naraku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:51.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:54.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then does Naraku care about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He doesn't want to acknowledge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But there's a lingering feeling for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:06.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he's trying to erase that\nfeeling by getting rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Enough, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have replenished myself\nwith lost souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You aren't planning to destroy\NNaraku alone, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:24.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:28.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is in love with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't stand the thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so late! Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:41.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess Inuyasha would\nhave calmed down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are those lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha and Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:04.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened in my absence?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:10.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't care how you feel\nabout me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:13.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will not let Naraku have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:17.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only I can protect you from Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Are you... crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:44.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will be the one to slay Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So... you don't have to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:50.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:51.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Men are such fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They believe that as long\nas they embrace a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she belongs to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kikyo?\N- Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watching you now,\NI realize that so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:20.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as Onigumo's heart\nexists inside Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:22.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there will be an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:27.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will use that chance to purify Naraku\nand totally destroy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:29.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:34.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:43.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once the thread of fate is tangled,\nit cannot be undone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Envy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:07.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A human emotion from the heart\nof that simpering fool Onigumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:09.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lost souls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sister Kikyo...is she nearby?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:51.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome! Were you watching?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:56.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha is looking straight at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:22:00.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How? How can he not avert his eyes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:49.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha has sworn to protect Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:51.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't stay by him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:53.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I ran back to the present world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.17,0:23:56.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I still have a fragment\nof the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I should return it to\nthe Feudal Era...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:00.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but if I return it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:03.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then it will really mean\nthe end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:07.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I stand in front of the sacred tree\nwhere I first met Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:12.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Back to Where We First Met"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:14.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
